seprhou.logic

Class FlightPlanGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • seprhou.logic.FlightPlanGenerator

  • public class FlightPlanGenerator
extends Object
    The default flight plan generator which controls introducing aircraft into the game

    This class contains many configuration parameters affecting generated flight paths. To use this class properly, call the setter for all the options which you want to change after creating this class.

      • makeFlightPlanNow

        public FlightPlan makeFlightPlanNow(Airspace airspace)
        Creates a new flight plan immediately (without taking timers into account)

        This is like makeFlightPlan(Airspace, float) but will try to make one now even if the configuration doesn't want to now. This may still return null however if it is not even possible to generate a path without impossible to avoid collisions.

        Parameters:
        airspace - the airspace the aircraft will be created in
        Returns:
        the new flight plan or null if no aircraft should be created now
        See Also:
        makeFlightPlan(Airspace, float)

      • makeFlightPlan

        public FlightPlan makeFlightPlan(Airspace airspace,
                        float delta)
        Creates a new flight plan

        This method uses all its various configuration settings to create a sutible flight plan. It does not generate a flight plan every time it is called however.

        Parameters:
        airspace - the airspace the aircraft will be created in
        Returns:
        the new flight plan or null if no aircraft should be created now
